Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:48.00,SongJap,,0,0,0,,時間が止まる 光と空の森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:48.00,SongChn,,0,0,0,,光线和天空的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:53.34,SongChn,,0,0,0,,风儿传递着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:59.35,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K90}ka{\K80}ze {\K60}ga {\K50}ha{\K50}ko{\K50}bu  {\K120}{\K65}ka{\K65}su{\K65}ka {\K60}na {\K60}se{\K40}se{\K40}ra{\K60}gi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:59.35,SongJap,,0,0,0,,風が運ぶ かすかなせせらぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:59.35,SongChn,,0,0,0,,细细的溪流声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:10.77,SongChn,,0,0,0,,你看闪闪发光的湖面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:10.77,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K85}ho{\K85}ra  {\K60}{\K50}ma{\K40}bu{\K40}shi{\K40}ku {\K80}{\K80}hi{\K75}ka{\K110}ru {\K85}mi{\K40}zuu{\K65}mi {\K80}wa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:10.77,SongJap,,0,0,0,,ほら まぶしく光る湖は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:25.21,SongChn,,0,0,0,,成为镜子映出那天失去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:17.97,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K120}ano {\K60}hi {\K70}ni {\K60}{\K50}na{\K40}ku{\K40}shi{\K60}ta {\K60}mo{\K50}no {\K60}wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:17.97,SongJap,,0,0,0,,あの日に失くしたものを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:25.21,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K60}utsu{\K60}shi{\K60}da{\K60}su {\K50}{\K40}ka{\K40}ga{\K60}mi {\K200}ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:25.21,SongJap,,0,0,0,,映し出す鏡に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:35.19,SongChn,,0,0,0,,幸福一定和悲哀很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:35.19,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K80}kit{\K60}to {\K30}shi{\K30}a{\K20}wa{\K20}se {\K200}wa {\K80}{\K60}ka{\K50}na{\K50}shi{\K50}mi {\K30}ni {\K30}ni{\K30}tei{\K90}ru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:35.19,SongJap,,0,0,0,,きっと幸せは 哀しみに似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:43.23,SongChn,,0,0,0,,闭上心灵的瞳眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:53.34,SongRom,,0,0,0,,{\K60}ko{\K60}ko{\K60}ro {\K100}no {\K70}hi{\K50}to{\K50}mi {\K60}to{\K40}ji{\K70}te  {\K60}{\K70}so{\K70}tto {\K80}{\K70}so{\K70}ra {\K110}wo {\K110}da{\K220}ku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:53.34,SongJap,,0,0,0,,心の瞳閉じて そっと空を抱く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:53.34,SongChn,,0,0,0,,轻轻地拥抱天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,下一回也一定要看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最优先事项喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,高二的暑假尾声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我一边感觉到\N我的心中破了一个大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一边活在当下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同学，大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天起，我是这个班的导师\N我叫风见瑞穗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对，由于跟老师的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我又再度加速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,草薙桂\N与风见瑞穗的兴奋体验
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,星空的邂逅下一回\N“再来一次，老师”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最优先事项喔
